      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires the Director of Taxation to appoint a legal, tax, or accounting professional as an Administrative Rules Officer.  Authorizes the Administrative Rules Officer to appoint individuals with suitable experience as Administrative Rules Specialists."
